  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition" : [ {
    "@value" : "Structured summary of genomic testing results generated from a molecular diagnostic assay (e.g., NGS panel, whole-exome sequencing)..A genomics report details the analysis of an individual's DNA or RNA, identifying genetic variations and their clinical implications. It typically includes variant classifications, associated gene-disease risks, and personalized treatment or preventative recommendations."
  } ]
