  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition" : [ {
    "@value" : "Rhabdomyosarcoma (RMS) is defined by SNOMED CT under the hierarchy of malignant neoplasms and disorders. While there is no single SNOMED code for a \"risk assessment,\" the concept is represented through standardized clinical criteria that measure tumor severity and prognosis."
